Face off against relentless Bacterian forces in GRADIUS ORIGINS, a collection that brings together six legendary arcade classics and the all-new SALAMANDER III. This collection also includes the long-awaited Gradius III AM Show version! Pilot your ship through dangerous enemy lines, upgrade your weapons, and master intense, fast-paced gameplay.

description:
Introducing GAIA, the robotic mech with devastating powers. Turn the tables on your enemies as you consume them to grow from prey to the apex predator and embrace your true purpose.

Shadow Labyrinth is a 2D action platformer and a genre-twisting alternate take on PAC-MAN. As Swordsman No. 8, awoken by a floating yellow orb, PUCK, you are chosen to become the instrument of its will. To survive, you must eat.

Coming July 18th on Xbox Series XIS.

Digital Pre-Orders start now: https://www.xbox.com/egames/store/shadow-labyrinth-pre-order/9n3d1mf47wx3
